OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780495872
OL,3,CMusic video campaign highlights value
OL,4,Cof keeping parents close to sick
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,FThe Hawes are now among the families
OL,8,Ffeatured in a new music video campaign
OL,9,Fhighlighting the importance of keeping
OL,10,Fparents close to sick children.
OL,12,FAiden, Theo's dad, said: "He was born
OL,13,Fwith Hypoxic-ischemic encephalopathy
OL,14,F(HIE) which ultimately is oxygen
OL,15,Fdeprivation to the brain close to or
OL,16,Fat the time of birth.
OL,18,F"He was born not breathing, he was put
OL,19,Fon a ventilator and critically for
OL,20,FTheo, he was put on a hypothermic
OL,21,Fcooling matt.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780495872
OL,3,CMusic video campaign highlights value
OL,4,Cof keeping parents close to sick
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,F"Given Theo's state, the
OL,8,Frecommendation was to get him to a
OL,9,Fhospital where not only did they have
OL,10,Fmore of the hypothermic matt, but they
OL,11,Fcould keep him in a stable
OL,12,Fenvironment."
OL,14,FBut Arrowe Park was a 72-mile round
OL,15,Ftrip. It was one of the nurses who
OL,16,Ftold the couple about Ronald McDonald
OL,17,FHouse, set up for families just like
OL,18,Ftheirs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780495872
OL,3,CMusic video campaign highlights value
OL,4,Cof keeping parents close to sick
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,FRochelle, Theo's Mum said having this
OL,8,Foption just above the ward was
OL,9,F"amazing" and that it "gave us a base
OL,10,Fto be close to him" and was also
OL,11,Fsomewhere for their daughter to come
OL,12,Ftoo.
OL,14,FShe continued: "Everything was
OL,15,Fchanging so quickly with his
OL,16,Fmedications and each day was so
OL,17,Fdifferent so we needed to be close to
OL,18,Fhim so it did just take that pressure
OL,19,Foff."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780495872
OL,3,CMusic video campaign highlights value
OL,4,Cof keeping parents close to sick
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,FThe Hawes were there for two weeks and
OL,8,Fonce they left, another family entered.
OL,10,FKatie Knight, House Manager, Ronal
OL,11,FMcDonald House, Arrowe Park: "Here at
OL,12,Fthe Ronald McDonald house in Arrow
OL,13,FPark, we support about 80-90 families
OL,14,Fper year. So we support practically
OL,15,Fwith our accommodation offer, but we
OL,16,Falso support with the emotional
OL,17,Fchallenges that families face.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
