PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780495872
OL,3,CMusic video campaign highlights value
OL,4,Cof keeping parents close to sick
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,F"So giving them a place to stay,
OL,8,Fconnect with each other, and rest and
OL,9,Fre-charge so they can be the best
OL,10,Fversions of themselves that aids their
OL,11,Fchild's recovery everyday."
OL,13,FThe Hawes family feature in the Ronald
OL,14,FMcDonald House music video with Pixie
OL,15,FLott, alongside other families, to
OL,16,Fraise awareness of the distances
OL,17,Ftravelled.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
