PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780495872
OL,3,CMusic video campaign highlights value
OL,4,Cof keeping parents close to sick
OL,5,Cchildren
OL,7,F"Last year, Ronald McDonald tracked
OL,8,Fthat the average distance that
OL,9,Ffamilies have to travel to see their
OL,10,Fchildren when they see their children
OL,11,Fwhen they're in hospital is 79miles.
OL,12,FSo the original obviously had a
OL,13,Fdifferent number of miles but it's a
OL,14,Fvery catchy song to remind people of
OL,15,Fthe impact of being able to stay on
OL,16,Fsite."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
